title: Paul McKenna & Michael Breen - Fast Phobia Cure
description:
Paul McKenna (born 8 November 1963, in Enfield, Middlesex) is an English hypnotist and self-improvement author. According to the Sunday Times he is Britain's best selling non-fiction author and is published in 30 languages.[1]

McKenna has written and produced books and multimedia products, hosted self-improvement television shows and presents seminars in hypnosis, neuro-linguistic programming and weight loss.
McKenna has also released a number of videos including Sleep Like a Log, Stop Smoking for Good, Supreme-Self-Confidence, Fast Phobia Cure..
